biography: Janne is a talented golfer who hails from Revontuli Golf.  He brings a wealth of experience to the Hector Trophée, having previously competed in the 2025, 2024, and 2022 editions of this prestigious invitational.

While Janne has yet to claim victory in the Hector Trophée, his consistent participation speaks volumes about his dedication and skill.  He’s a player to watch, possessing the talent to contend for both the coveted Hector Trophée and the individual Victor trophy.
